# Azure OpenAI

Primary metrics from Azure's OpenAI service. This dashboard contains: 

- Request rates
- Error rates
- Token usage
- Chat completion latency

embeddableConfig.description: Number of calls made to the Azure OpenAI API over a period of time. Applies to PTU, PTU-Managed and Pay-as-you-go deployments.
Total number of calls with error response (HTTP response code 4xx or 5xx).

panelsJSON.title: Overall request rate - by model deployment
Overall error rate - by response code

embeddableConfig.description: Processed prompt token (input) and Generated completion token (output).
